Package algorithms.shortestPaths

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStar
    An implementation of the A* algorithm using the "uniform cost search" pattern and heuristics given to the code.
    BeamSearch
    from https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Beam_search Beam Search uses a greedy, breadth-first search to build its search tree, but only keeps top k (beam size) nodes at each level in memory.
    BellmanFord
    solves the single source shortest paths problem.
